      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know what to do anymore. the company is gone, the liquidators are calling every hour, and the debt is just... it's impossible. i lost everything. i can't even think about going back home and looking my parents in the eye. the shame is just too much. i feel like there's no way out of this.",
